{
  "id": "69b710b413a9a3cfb7eb3f55",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:自分の身の振り方を考える時",
  "created": 1773605079,
  "updated": 1773607085,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b710b413a9a3cfb7eb3f55",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:自分の身の振り方を考える時",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605079,
      "updated": 1773605079
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d700000000008a4ff4",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605079,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ff5",
      "text": "ねえねえ二人とも～。今日のテーマなんだけどさ、「[自分の身の振り方を考える時]」ってやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ff6",
      "text": "高校生的にも、わりとガチテーマじゃね？進路とか将来とかさ～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ff7",
      "text": "うちらもそろそろ「この先どうする？」みたいなイベント発生してるし。人生RPGの分岐ポイントって感じｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ff8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ff9",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ffa",
      "text": "（微笑）そうね。人生を物語にたとえるなら、ちょうど章の変わり目のようなものかもしれません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ffb",
      "text": "静かな夜に本を閉じたあと、登場人物の行く末を思うように、自分の未来をそっと考えてしまう……そんな時がございますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ffc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ffd",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4ffe",
      "text": "確かに。進路選択は意思決定プロセスの一種。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a4fff",
      "text": "簡単に言うと「いくつかの道の中から、いちばん良さそうなものを選ぶ作業」だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5000",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5001",
      "text": "意思決定の基本は三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5002",
      "text": " 1. 目標を定義する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5003",
      "text": " 2. 選択肢を列挙する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5004",
      "text": " 3. 情報をもとに比較する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5005",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5006",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5007",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Decision-making",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5008",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5009",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a500a",
      "text": "おお、りかのガチ解説きたｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a500b",
      "text": "でもさー、現実ってそんなキレイに整理できなくない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a500c",
      "text": "「好きなことやりたいけど食えるの？」とかさ、「安定だけどテンション上がらん…」とか。完全にバグってる選択画面だよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a500d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a500e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a500f",
      "text": "それは正常な状態。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5010",
      "text": "人間の意思決定には不確実性がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5011",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5012",
      "text": "要するに「未来が完全には分からない」という問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5013",
      "text": "だから合理的な人でも迷う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5014",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5015",
      "text": "ちなみにこの分野では期待値という考え方がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5016",
      "text": "ざっくり言うと「[$ 成功する確率 \\times 得られるメリット]」で判断する方法。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5017",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5018",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expected_value",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5019",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a501a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a501b",
      "text": "期待値！？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a501c",
      "text": "ゲームでいうと「[$ レアドロ確率 \\times 装備の強さ]」みたいな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a501d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a501e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a501f",
      "text": "その理解でだいたい合ってる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5020",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5021",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5022",
      "text": "なるほどね～。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5023",
      "text": "でもさ、人生ガチャって確率表見えなくね？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5024",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5025",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5026",
      "text": "（小さく笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5027",
      "text": "確かに、人生には攻略本がありませんものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5028",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5029",
      "text": "けれど私は、少し違う考え方も好きです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a502a",
      "text": "自分の身の振り方を考えるとき、「この道が正しいか」よりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a502b",
      "text": "「この道を歩いたら、どんな景色が見えるのかしら」と想像するのです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a502c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a502d",
      "text": "それは、旅の行き先を決めるときのようなもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a502e",
      "text": "どちらの町にも、それぞれの美しさがありますから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a502f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5030",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5031",
      "text": "おお～、あや文学モードだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5032",
      "text": "でもちょっとわかるかも。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5033",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5034",
      "text": "「どっちが正解？」って考えると詰むけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5035",
      "text": "「どっちが楽しそう？」なら選べる気がする！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5036",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5037",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5038",
      "text": "興味深い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5039",
      "text": "それは価値観ベースの意思決定だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a503a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a503b",
      "text": "つまり「合理的に最適」ではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a503c",
      "text": "「自分の価値観に合う」かどうかで決める方法。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a503d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a503e",
      "text": "実際、キャリア研究でも重要視されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a503f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5040",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5041",
      "text": "https://hbr.org/2016/01/how-to-make-better-decisions-about-your-career",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5042",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5043",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5044",
      "text": "へぇ～、ちゃんと研究あるんだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5045",
      "text": "なんか安心したｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5046",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5047",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5048",
      "text": "人の道は、誰かが用意した一本の線ではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5049",
      "text": "それぞれが歩きながら形づくる小径のようなものなのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a504a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a504b",
      "text": "迷うことも、立ち止まることも、きっと無駄ではありません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a504c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a504d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a504e",
      "text": "要点を一度整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a504f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5050",
      "text": "自分の身の振り方を考えるときの視点は大きく三つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5051",
      "text": " 1. 合理的判断（確率やメリットで考える）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5052",
      "text": " 2. 価値観（自分が大事にしたいこと）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5053",
      "text": " 3. 体験の想像（その道でどんな人生になるか）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5054",
      "text": "この三つを組み合わせると、判断の精度が上がる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5055",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5056",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5057",
      "text": "さすがまとめ役ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5058",
      "text": "てかさ、結局さ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5059",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a505a",
      "text": "「完璧な選択」ってないけど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a505b",
      "text": "「納得できる選択」は作れるって感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a505c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a505d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a505e",
      "text": "ええ、とても素敵な言い方ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a505f",
      "text": "人生の物語を綴るのは、自分自身ですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5060",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5061",
      "text": "どの章を選んでも、その人なりの意味が生まれるのだと思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5062",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5063",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5064",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5065",
      "text": "最適解よりも更新可能な選択をするのが現実的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5066",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5067",
      "text": "つまり、あとで方向転換できる道を選ぶこと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5068",
      "text": "ソフトウェア開発でも同じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5069",
      "text": "変更可能な設計が強い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a506a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a506b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a506c",
      "text": "人生もアップデート前提のゲームか～！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a506d",
      "text": "なるほど、それなら気楽かも。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a506e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a506f",
      "text": "とりあえず今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5070",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5071",
      "text": "「人生は一本道じゃないし、あとでパッチ当てられる！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5072",
      "text": "ってことでどう？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5073",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5074",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5075",
      "text": "（笑いながらうなずく）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5076",
      "text": "ええ、それはとても希望のある結論ですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5077",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5078",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a5079",
      "text": "悪くないまとめ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a507a",
      "text": "バージョンアップ可能な人生設計。合理的だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a507b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a507c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a507d",
      "text": "よっしゃ、じゃあ今日の鼎談はここまで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a507e",
      "text": "次回テーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b710d800000000008a507f",
      "text": "「将来AIに仕事奪われる問題」とか？それとも「神アニメランキング」？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773605080,
      "updated": 1773605080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b718a00000000000b9dfb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773607073,
      "updated": 1773607073
    },
    {
      "id": "69b718a10000000000b9dfb2",
      "text": "#2026-03-16",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773607073,
      "updated": 1773607085
    },
    {
      "id": "69b718a30000000000b9dfb3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773607075,
      "updated": 1773607075
    }
  ]
}